README.md 👋 B1k1 A python utility for taking backups and with the option to upload to Google Drive.
Installation &amp; Usage: Follow these steps: 1st: git clone https://github.com/Xeroxxhah/B1k1.git 2nd: cd B1k1 3rd: pip install --upgrade google-api-python-client google-auth-httplib2 google-auth-oauthlib 4th: Configure config.json 5th python3 b1k1.py Configuring config.json &ldquo;paths&rdquo; = &ldquo;Pths which you want to take backup of&rdquo; i.e &ldquo;/home/username/&rdquo;
&ldquo;backup_path&rdquo; = &ldquo;path where you want to store backup&rdquo; i.e &ldquo;/home/username/&rdquo;
&ldquo;gd_sk_path&rdquo; = &ldquo;Path of Creddentails.
